  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Send 1000 Children living with Tigers to School</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In India, a lack of education contributes to the tigers&apos; decline via critical habitat destruction and poaching. Rural villages are highly dependent on farming. Children often don&apos;t go to school due to the high cost of learning materials. Long-term prospects are poor as children lack critical literacy skills and awareness of forest ecology. Tigers4Ever&apos;s provision of 1000 education packs to Bandhavgarh&apos;s children will help improve future outcomes with literacy skills and environmental awareness.</narrative>
  </description>
